                                            <h2>FAO Head Quarters</h2>

                                            <p>ESN - Nutrition Division:
                                                Catherine Leclercq and Pauline Allemand are currently designing the tool, with the collaboration of Ruth Charrondière in terms of link with food composition data and in collaboration with Yvette Fautsch and Yenory for the qualitative surveys related to the participatory development of the tool
                                                ESS - Statistics Division:
                                                Fabio Grita and his team (Francesca Rosa, Fabrizio Castelli, Nicola Selleri, Daniele Salvatore and Ivano Cortesini) are currently developing the data management system and dissemination platform. There is also a current collaboration with Piero Conforti and Nathalie Troubat to develop nutrition indicators that are common to  individual and household surveys
                                                AGDF - Food Safety and Quality Unit:
                                                Markus Lipp, Mary Kenny, Sarah Cahill and Jean Charles Leblanc are currently collaborating to the selection of indicators in the field of food safety</p>
